def daqlib.createUnits (   mngr,
  daqUnits,
  model 
)

Registers DAQ units with the database.

This function registers each DAQ unit as a DaqUnit object, with DaqUnitChannel objects. To each DaqUnitChannel a DaqUnitChannelData signal object is attached, that will hold the raw sensor data.

Parameters:
mngr SenStore database manager proxy
daqUnits dictionary with configured DAQ units
model name of DAQ units model
See also:
